The paper proposes a method for leveraging communities and other topological features for use in a predictive classification task. This suggests that the paper could belong to the sub-categories of Social and Information Networks (cs.SI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Statistical Learning (cs.SD), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI).
